headline: GoDaddy Inc. to Present at Citi's 2025 Global TMT Conference
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE: GDDY) Chief Financial Officer Mark McCaffrey will present at Citi's 2025 Global TMT Conference in New York City on Wednesday, Sept. 3, 2025, at 8:50 a.m. ET / 5:50 a.m. PT.
